No. —. Original.

Ex parte: In the Matter of Clair D. Vallette and Alfred B. Quinton, Petitioners. Submitted October 9, 1916. Decided October 16, 1916.

Petition for a hearing on motion for leave to file bill of complaint in the name of The United States v. The State of Florida denied. Mr. Alfred B. Quinton and Mr. Clair D. Vallette for the petitioners.
